### EduPortal API - Performance Controller
### Student performance tracking endpoints (Not yet implemented)
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/performance
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### GET ALL PERFORMANCE RECORDS - (Admin, Danışman, Öğretmen)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET PERFORMANCE BY ID
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET PERFORMANCE BY STUDENT
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET PERFORMANCE BY COURSE - (Admin, Öğretmen, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### CREATE PERFORMANCE RECORD - (Admin, Öğretmen)
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "courseId": 1,
  "score": 85.5,
  "period": "2024-2025 Güz",
  "notes": "İyi performans"
}

### ===========================================
### UPDATE PERFORMANCE RECORD - (Admin, Öğretmen)
### ===========================================
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "score": 90.0,
  "notes": "Performans güncellendi"
}

### ===========================================
### DELETE PERFORMANCE RECORD - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

